Results.ReviewText:
These flip-flops are really wonderful for the price that you pay. Every year I always buy one of each color!! They are comfortable, and last longer then other similar & competitive products. The colors ad a great POP to your outfit, and make it fun. The ONLY ‘bad’ thing is the lack of color choices. I mean, if you look at the women’s flip-flops, there are at least 20 different colors including 2 yellows, 3 greens, 3 blues and even a teal, just to name a few. I wear a size 11-12 in men’s shoe sizes, and the women’s flip-slops only go up to size 11, witch is size 9 in men’s, so I’m limited to what you offer in the men’s sizes.
Old Navy, if you made more color choices, I guarantee you I would buy them all! These are my FAVORITE flip-flops!!!
Results.Title: ***MORE COLORS PLEASE!!!!!***
